@Lucy_Kinski Hallo Lucy, 
wir möchten uns für die entstandenen Umstände bei dir entschuldigen. Bitte sende uns deinen Buchungscode als PM, damit wir die an dieser Stelle weiterhelfen können.
Liebe Grüße, Shawn

@feuerkind99 Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. The online check-in is available 47 hours before departure. However, your luggage can be checked in only at the airport. Please use the fast drop zone. You can get your baggage tag from several machines in terminal 3
Best regards, Shawn

@ziryansalayi Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code, so we can take a closer. Many thanks.
Best regards, Shawn

@inga_danielyan Hi Inga, 
We are very sorry to have caused you so much trouble during your trip. Please send us any claims for compensation via the following link https://t.co/1jYyfcuAde Many thanks for your understanding and patience. 
Best regards, Shawn

@Manino_19 Hi there, 
Please send us your booking code as a PM, so we can take a closer look. Many thanks.
Best regards, Shawn

@bruja_baby @Lufthansa_USA Hi there, 
Please accept our apology for all the trouble caused due to the delay. Please send us your booking code as PM, so we can take a closer look. Many thanks.
Best regards, Shawn

@AHeathrow @lufthansa Hi there, 
Please send us your booking via PM, as we would like to take a closer look into your request.
Best regards, Shawn

@rstapley74 Hi Rob, 
Unfortunately, we cannot tell you exactly when you will receive a response since your case has to be handled by various different departments. Still, we can assure you that our colleagues are doing their best to get back to you as soon as possible.  
Best regards, Shawn

@EmilyQCalle Hi Emily, 
We are sorry for all the trouble you have experienced lately. Please send us your booking code as PM, so we can take a closer look. 
Best regards, Shawn

@butiregress  [2/2] ... which you will have received at the Lost &amp; Found counter at the airport. Otherwise, if you do not have a PIR please fill out the form here:
https://t.co/paWor4omhC
Best regards, Denis

@pedg Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code, so we can take a closer look. Many thanks.
Best regards, Shawn

@jakobmaul [2/2] 
Bitte sende uns deinen Buchungscode, damit wir dir an dieser Stelle besser helfen können. 
Liebe Grüße, Shawn

@loshtwala Hi Losh, 
Please send us your receipt via the following link https://t.co/1jYyfcuAde - on here you have to fill up the online form, where you can also attach your receipt. Many thanks.
Best regards, Shawn

@cypriotka @lufthansa Hi there, 
We have replied to your DM, please check your inbox. 
Best regards, Shawn

@twitjawy Hi,
I am very sorry to hear about your experience. I kindly ask you to please send an official complaint to our Customer Relations. Please use the contact form on our website. The colleagues will gladly do the necessary research.
Best regards, Alessandra

@nevahybred Hi there, 
We are sorry that you had difficulty contacting us by phone. Due to the current situation, unfortunately, all our channels are overloaded and there may be longer waiting times. Please send your request to specialcases@austrian.com
Best regards, Shawn

@Annika_Hofman @martinjan Hallo Annika, 
Wir möchten uns bei dir für die Umstände entschuldigen. Bitte fülle das online Formular über den folgenden Link https://t.co/YRTi6bIUO2  und wähle anschließend die Thematik Flugunregelmäßigkeit. Vielen Dank für dein Verständnis.  
Liebe Grüße, Shawn
